features: THE MULTIPLE PACK FRIENDSHIP: Boys and girls can imagine incredible space adventures alongside Groot, Marvel's Cosmo and Baby Rocket! This trio may seem adorable, but it's nothing short of heroic
GROOT DELUXE ACTION FIGURES: the pack contains a 4" Groot action figure with a removable wing accessory, removable root arms with blaster function and 2 rocket accessories for epic galaxy adventures

MARVEL 'S COSMO: the exclusive and adorable Marvel's Cosmo in spacesuit from the movie "Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3"" features multiple pivot points to pose the 2" action figure and imagine space adventures
BABY ROCKET: So small and so cute! Thanks to this little action figure, boys and girls can play Baby Rocket as they take part in heroic battles alongside Groot and Marvel's Cosmo

COLLECT OTHER TOYS AND ACTION GUARDIANS OF THE GALAXY FIGURES - Don't miss out on other Guardians of the Galaxy action figures and toys, inspired by Universe Marvel (each sold separately, subject to availability)
body.description: Boys and girls aged 4 and up can explore space and create their own adventures among galaxies with these Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3" - Inspired by the Marvel Universe This package contains a 10cm scale Groot action figure with wings and blaster accessories, along with a 2-inch Marvel's Cosmo action figure and a 1.5cm Baby Rocket action figure for full of fun and action between galaxies! Boys and girls will look forward to posing these action figures to imagine adventures and space battles. Copyright 2023 Marvel. Hasbro and all related terms are trademarks of Hasbro.
